<span style="font-size: x-small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20060720174929/http://www.thepeacealliance.org/content/view/50/127/">and many more...</a></span> 
</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		</table>
		</td>

